{"tid":2478331,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月9地鳴] 進擊的巨人漫畫139話 - 等候區（4）創狗落地獄未","createTime":"2021-04-07T03:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:44:39.000Z","uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bfdf5ee0e0f18e67f4ce0586d6221132e0b0663a","tid":2478331,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"創狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeded13e6c096dec49bd7cd8451db524a1ab9057","tid":2478331,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXa84ZgEhL9gbGgZQSxFHS4Hb7z9bzAumTyX1NfDa4aeu?filename=SBiQ1Jq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBiQ1Jq.jpg&h=73b9db92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似係新圖透"},{"pid":"7d12a11caa4e5630b3889c46f15c3c9d09ee92f2","tid":2478331,"uid":185217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:38.000Z","msg":"我諗問題係現實世界睇得出仇恨 報復 欺詐<br />\n依啲嘢係冇停過(S1-4)都有講過<br />\n所以如果蟲仔死咗之後<br />\n100%世界和平就會好夾硬嚟<br />\n<br />\n另外如果成功滅世得翻島內人<br />\n島内啲人遲早爭巨人咪又係戰爭同唔自由<br />\n艾倫應該唔會想咁<br />\n<br />\n解放咗ymir curse<br />\n令艾人自由多咗 但並非全和平<br />\n咁就叫做合理"},{"pid":"28dd2c0430df8eb5bbcbf2f9dd1d556f9f40908d","tid":2478331,"uid":201601,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"啲人問點解爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌成班反派bbq仲唔爛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d54a14574a869873d18ad098e91e5c65b71b67d","tid":2478331,"uid":315251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"我之前已經講咗<br />\n每個人對神作嘅定義唔同<br />\n以下係某啲人嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\n1.完得太快<br />\n好多時候要讀者腦補 但每個人諗嘅唔同<br />\n好聽啲叫有想像空間 難聽啲係內容不足<br />\n<br />\n2.人物刻劃不足<br />\n艾撚後期side character<br />\n就算139補多個艾敏對話都彌補唔到<br />\n<br />\n3.打戲太多 文戲太少<br />\n有人覺得歷代巨人出曬嚟打係多餘<br />\n純粹創哥想要場面<br />\n<br />\n4.有好多bug 都解釋唔充分<br />\n例如 法仔第一次變巨人就運用自如<br />\n點解三笠咁快就知艾撚係口入面<br />\n不過創哥話點就點<br />\n<br />\n5.讀者覺得噁心 被背叛<br />\n咦個係個人情感<br />\n但你諗下島內人被warrior殺咗咁多<br />\n調查兵團死咗咁多人<br />\n但Warriors就冇事 bbq <br />\nJean Reiner有講有笑<br />\n部分讀者接受唔到係正常"},{"pid":"b6f33c7b6dc77cd8aae44b37c6a97c09777e0b29","tid":2478331,"uid":1938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:42:46.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8b6acd808c7c7bd7b84ab6e05e3ad2fc3a23453e","tid":2478331,"uid":325757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28dd2c0430df8eb5bbcbf2f9dd1d556f9f40908d","tid":2478331,"uid":201601,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"啲人問點解爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌成班反派bbq仲唔爛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"套嘢唔係話無絕對正義同邪惡咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瑪雷眼中艾倫都係反派嚟 第三季嘅角度 佢依家都就死/死咗咁款"},{"pid":"4c7a4c889272bba8adcbe1047b29049d89b6133e","tid":2478331,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeded13e6c096dec49bd7cd8451db524a1ab9057","tid":2478331,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBiQ1Jq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBiQ1Jq.jpg&h=73b9db92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似係新圖透"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"咁睇的話個情報係真左九成<br />\n艾倫同阿爾敏又入左個空間鳩UP"},{"pid":"1e68048a94f9c9b146256e1d1a4dd8c41b84e6f3","tid":2478331,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d54a14574a869873d18ad098e91e5c65b71b67d","tid":2478331,"uid":315251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco